    "description": "The Oracle StorageTek T10000D Tape Drive blends the highest capacity, performance, reliability, and data security to support demanding, 24/7 data center operations. The StorageTek T10000D Tape Drive delivers the world's fastest write speeds up to 8.5 TB of magnetic tape storage; making it ideal for data center operations with growing volumes. Designed for maximum performance, the drive allows the use of multiple keys per tape with a cache memory to minimize the overhead of key transmission. Works seamlessly with the Oracle Key Manager to provide a secure end-to-end management solution.",
